{
  "stem": "3721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were not allowed to go to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had to sit in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were allowed to go out only a certain hour of the day to the market, to buy food, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But anyway, they already were beating up people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If they were Jewish, if they caught them, for no reason at all they would just beat them up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that time, but later on, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they started collecting the Jews into the ghetto, that's when I was beaten up very badly by somebody that I knew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the amazing thing about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the reason for that is because I had a girlfriend who was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was my father's dental assistant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And her father was a top Nazi in our hometown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was actually, she was actually Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And her father was a member of the Hungarian Nazi party, the Arrow Cross they called them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was the head of the Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yet, she was really, I believe, very friendly with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Probably more than that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was in love with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the father, of course-- the family forbade her to see me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was a pretty girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she had a non-Jewish boyfriend who was a year older than me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, don't forget, I was myself only about 18 years old, and she was, like, 17.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But, he knew that I used to see her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was warned not to see her, and I didn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she came to see me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he got very-- he saw us once talk together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, I guess, he decided to take revenge on it when the Nazis closed all of the ghetto and they were collecting the Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
